perl-xml-twig: perl-xml-twig (Perl module for processing huge XML documents in tree mode)
perl-xml-twig:
perl-xml-twig: This module provides a way to process XML documents. It is build on
perl-xml-twig: top of XML::Parser.  XML::Twig offers a tree interface to the
perl-xml-twig: document, while allowing you to output the parts of it that have been
perl-xml-twig: completely processed. It allows minimal resource (CPU and memory)
perl-xml-twig: usage by building the tree only for the parts of the documents that
perl-xml-twig: need actual processing, through the use of the twig_roots and
perl-xml-twig: twig_print_outside_roots options.
perl-xml-twig: http://search.cpan.org/dist/XML-Twig/
perl-xml-twig: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
